.TH "CLIFM" "1" "Jul 11, 2022" "clifm 1.6.1" "CLIFM Manual"
.SH NAME
clifm \- The Command Line File Manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B clifm
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]... [\fI\,PATH\/\fR]

